cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with improving the invariance of CNN activations for recognition tasks. It may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories as it proposes a new scheme for feature extraction that improves the discriminative power of CNN activations. Additionally, it may belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) categories as it demonstrates the effectiveness of the proposed scheme for image classification and instance-level retrieval tasks.
